==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Toothwort
<hw>Tooth"wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A plant whose roots are fancied to resemble teeth, as certain
plants of the genus <gen>Lathraea</gen>, and various species of
<gen>Dentaria</gen>. See <er>Coralwort</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Toothy</ent>⟦br⟧
